          Updated {updatedDate}. Search/scrape sources included BrightData Google
          searches, BrightData page scraping, regular web search and Google Places API
          data collected server-side. The embedded map uses the browser credential.
          Public pages and Google reviews can change quickly; verify current credentials,
          pricing, complications policy and who performs each procedure.
        </p>
